    "body": "This one needs to be further broken down into features as it's too large and difficult to action.\r\nI would suggest:\r\n\r\nNotification on top of wallet view:\r\n\r\n```\r\nAs a user\r\nI want to see a notification when I access wallet to backup my seed phrase\r\nSo I don't forget to back it up\r\n```\r\nPop up\r\n```\r\nAs a user\r\nI want to be reminded to backup my seed phrase periodically \r\nSo I don't forget to back it up\r\n```\r\n\r\nEnforce backup\r\n\r\n```\r\nAs a user\r\nI want to be forced to backup my seed phrase after 30 days\r\nSo that I am sure that I can recover my funds\r\n```\r\n\r\nI am happy to do that if you'd like me to, let me know what you think @hesterbruikman \r\n",
